<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFA26A1DFD25974D1A2CBA98" pageId="89" pageNumber="847" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFA26A1DFD25974D1A2CBA98" blockId="89.[728,1321,276,703]" pageId="89" pageNumber="847">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFA26A1DFD25974D1DA9BA07" baseAuthorityName="de Winton" baseAuthorityYear="1901" box="[729,937,276,309]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="89" pageNumber="847" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="floweri">Eptesicus floweri</taxonomicName>
is often included in a separate subgenus, Rhinopterus, butits systematic position in relation to other 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFA26A1DFB49973F1B29BAB1" box="[1205,1321,358,387]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="89" pageNumber="847" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Eptesicus</taxonomicName>
